# 📋 Screenshot Data Extractor

Extract contact details (Name, Mobile, Email, UPI ID) from WhatsApp screenshots using **Google Gemini AI Vision**.

🔗 **Live Tool:** [Click here to use](https://YOUR-USERNAME.github.io/screenshot-extractor/extractor.html)
*(Replace YOUR-USERNAME with your GitHub username after deploying)*

---

## ✨ Features

- 📸 Upload multiple screenshots at once
- 🤖 AI-powered extraction using Google Gemini 1.5 Flash
- ✅ Reads numbers, names, emails, UPI IDs accurately
- 🔍 Duplicate number detection
- 📥 Download results as CSV or Excel (.xlsx)
- 📋 Copy individual columns (Names / Mobiles / Emails / UPI IDs)
- 🌙 Works with dark mode & light mode screenshots
- 🔒 API key stored in your browser only — never shared

---

## 🚀 How to Use

1. Open the live link above in your browser
2. Get a **free Gemini API key** from [aistudio.google.com/app/apikey](https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey)
   - Select **Gemini 1.5 Flash** model → **1,500 images/day free**
3. Paste your API key in the box → click **Save Key**
4. Upload your WhatsApp screenshots
5. Click **Extract from Screenshots**
6. Download as CSV or Excel

---

## ⚠️ Important

- **Never share your API key** with anyone
- Your API key is saved only in your own browser (localStorage)
- It is NOT stored in any file or server
- Free tier: **1,500 requests/day** with Gemini 1.5 Flash

